title: Hulk - Future Imperfect 01-02 (1992-1993|Digital|MM-Syl3ntBob)
description:
Two legends combine as Peter David writes and George Perez illustrates this crazy alternate reality tale. Promotional info from comicvine - "The Incredible Hulk travels to an apocalyptic future to face his ultimate challenge...himself. Meet the Maestro, the Hulk's future imperfect self. He's a despot who rules a nuclear ravaged world with gamma-fisted tyranny. Can even the Green Goliath defeat a foe whose strength rivals his own? A foe who knows his every move before he even makes it?"
